{"title":"眼睛和它们的朋友——为纪念六一国际儿童节而作","authors":["高士其"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛和它们的朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为纪念六一国际儿童节而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高士其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛和它们的朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最灵敏的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们非常忠实地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向大脑反映，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外界的情况。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形状、距离、颜色、方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在它们上面登记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美和丑，朋友和敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们都能认识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种文字和信号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们也都能知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光是眼睛的永久伴侣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们就不能照常工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在光的世界里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从星光、月光、到日光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从烛光、灯光、到电光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从五光十色的霓虹灯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到光芒万丈的探照灯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有透视人体的爱克斯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是眼睛的助手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镜也是眼睛的朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开镜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们的能力就要缩小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在镜的家庭里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有凸镜和凹镜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有望远镜和天文望远镜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有显微镜和电子显微镜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有电视机和雷达；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都为眼睛效劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大它们的视察范围。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是眼睛的保卫者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纠正它们的近视和远视的缺点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的能窥探宇宙的秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和星球的奥妙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的能侦察微生物的活动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭穿细菌的内幕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的能把各种现场上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所发生的事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通过无线电波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人们收看和收听；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的能把空中飞行的情形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向地面上通讯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了眼睛的便利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们早就发明了照相机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是眼睛的学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摹仿它们的构造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有底片、有暗箱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有镜头和开关；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有自动对光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结构越来越完善。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有电影机和幻灯机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是眼睛的同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们能把动人的科学故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在银幕上放映，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孩子们看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个是儿童节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最精彩的节目。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛和它们的朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为它们对于人类，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有特殊的贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年5月22日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}